<seg id="750">& dot; algorithm, the standard for directional graphs. it produces hierarchical or layered graphs of aligned graphene. the algorithm lays the edges in the same direction (from top to bottom or from left to right) and then tries to produce as short edges as possible and as few edges as possible.</seg>
